"1  shallot, thinly sliced","2 teaspoons olive oil","1  (12-oz.) package frozen dark, sweet pitted cherries, thawed","2 tablespoons balsamic vinegar","2 tablespoons honey","1/4 teaspoon chopped fresh rosemary","1/8 teaspoon salt","1/8 teaspoon pepper","2 cups loosely packed arugula","16  (1/4-inch-thick) ciabatta bread slices, toasted","1  (8-oz.) wedge blue cheese, thinly sliced*","  Garnish: freshly ground pepper"